<a href="/questions/1155382-i-really-enjoyed-this-book-i-loved">I really enjoyed this book. I loved learning about this incredible scientist, but also about how his life fit into history. I also loved how I learned a bit about the people he inspired (i.e. Darwin, Thoreau). Are there any other biographies like this that you would recommend? I am new to reading these types of books (I usually read historical fiction or fantasy), so you suggestions would really help.</a>
